All 6 features implemented and verified. Here's what changed:

**`app/auth.py`** — The `require_api_key` dependency now:
- Reads the `X-API-Key` header (defaults to `None` if absent)
- Raises `401` with "Invalid or missing API key" if missing or not in `VALID_API_KEYS`
- Returns the username on success

**`app/main.py`** — Six endpoints in total:

| Endpoint | Auth | Behavior |
|---|---|---|
| `GET /tasks?status=&priority=&assigned_to=&page=&page_size=` | No | Optional filtering (status, priority, assigned_to) + pagination (default page=1, page_size=20, max 100) |
| `POST /tasks` | Yes | Validates `project_id` (404 if not found), auto-generates ID via `max(id)+1`, returns 201 |
| `PUT /tasks/{task_id}` | Yes | Partial update via `TaskUpdate` with `exclude_unset=True`, 404 if not found |
| `DELETE /tasks/{task_id}` | Yes | Removes task from list, returns 204, 404 if not found |

